<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Bagphat Football Academy</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --green: #1a7a2e;
      --green-bright: #25b042;
      --gold: #f5c518;
      --dark: #0a0f0d;
      --dark2: #111a14;
      --white: #f0f4f1;
      --grey: #8a9e8f;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NOISE OVERLAY ── */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(10,15,13,0.95), transparent);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--white);
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--grey); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--green-bright); color: var(--dark);
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.6rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      padding: 8rem 4rem 4rem;
    }

    /* Field lines background */
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 70% 50%, rgba(26,122,46,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 79px, rgba(37,176,66,0.04) 79px, rgba(37,176,66,0.04) 80px),
        repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 79px, rgba(37,176,66,0.04) 79px, rgba(37,176,66,0.04) 80px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* Large field circle */
    .field-circle {
      position: absolute;
      right: -10vw; top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 65vw; height: 65vw;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(37,176,66,0.12);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: rotate 60s linear infinite;
    }
    .field-circle::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 10%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,24,0.07);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    @keyframes rotate { to { transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(360deg); } }

    .hero-tag {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green-bright);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s forwards;
    }
    .hero-tag::before {
      content: '';
      width: 36px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--green-bright);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      max-width: 700px;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title em {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--gold);
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--grey); max-width: 420px; line-height: 1.7;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s forwards;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s forwards;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--green-bright); color: var(--dark);
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1rem 2.4rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      clip-path: polygon(10px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 10px) 100%, 0% 100%);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-secondary {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--grey); background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .btn-secondary::before {
      content: '▶';
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--green-bright);
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: flex; gap: 4rem; margin-top: 5rem;
      opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1s forwards;
    }
    .stat-item {}
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-num span { color: var(--gold); }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--grey); margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ── MARQUEE ── */
    .marquee-wrapper {
      background: var(--green);
      padding: 0.9rem 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .marquee-track {
      display: flex; gap: 3rem;
      animation: marquee 25s linear infinite;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .marquee-item {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .marquee-dot { color: var(--gold); }
    @keyframes marquee { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

    /* ── SECTIONS ── */
    section { padding: 6rem 4rem; }
    .section-tag {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green-bright);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    /* ── PROGRAMS ── */
    #programs { background: var(--dark2); }
    .programs-header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    .programs-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5px;
    }
    .program-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .program-card:hover { background: rgba(26,122,46,0.12); }
    .program-card:hover .program-icon { color: var(--gold); }
    .program-num {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .program-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .program-name {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .program-desc {
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--grey); line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .program-age {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.2rem;
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green-bright);
      border: 1px solid rgba(37,176,66,0.3);
      padding: 0.25rem 0.8rem;
    }

    /* ── ABOUT ── */
    #about {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .about-visual {
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    }
    .about-box {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green) 0%, var(--dark2) 100%);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-box::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        -45deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 10px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 10px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 11px
      );
    }
    .about-accent {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1.5rem; right: -1.5rem;
      width: 60%; height: 60%;
      border: 2px solid var(--gold);
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .about-content .section-title { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .about-text {
      color: var(--grey); font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .about-pillars {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .pillar {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--green-bright);
      padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    }
    .pillar-name {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .pillar-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--grey); }

    /* ── COACHES ── */
    #coaches { background: var(--dark2); text-align: center; }
    #coaches .section-title { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    #coaches .section-sub {
      color: var(--grey); font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    .coaches-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .coach-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .coach-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); }
    .coach-avatar {
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--dark2));
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 1.2rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      border: 2px solid rgba(37,176,66,0.3);
    }
    .coach-name {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .coach-role {
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green-bright); margin: 0.3rem 0 0.8rem;
    }
    .coach-bio { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--grey); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── ENROLL CTA ── */
    #enroll {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green) 0%, #0d4a1a 100%);
      text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    #enroll::before {
      content: '⚽';
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 30vw;
      opacity: 0.05;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    #enroll .section-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    #enroll .section-sub {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 1rem;
      max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .enroll-form {
      display: flex; gap: 0; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .enroll-input {
      flex: 1;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-right: none;
      padding: 1rem 1.4rem;
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      outline: none;
    }
    .enroll-input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
    .enroll-btn {
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark);
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1rem 1.8rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .enroll-btn:hover { background: var(--white); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: #050807;
      padding: 3rem 4rem;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 900;
    }
    .footer-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; }
    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--grey);
      text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      section, .hero { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
      .programs-grid, .coaches-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      #about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
      .footer-links { flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
      .enroll-form { flex-direction: column; }
      .enroll-input { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-bottom: none; }
      .programs-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; }
      .about-visual { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">BAGPHAT <span>FA</span></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#programs">Programs</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#coaches">Coaches</a></li>
    <li><a href="#enroll">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-cta" onclick="document.getElementById('enroll').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Enroll Now</button>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="field-circle"></div>
  <div class="hero-tag">Bagphat, Uttar Pradesh</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    Build Your<br>
    <em>Legacy</em>
    on the Pitch
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    Elite football training for the next generation of champions. Discipline, skill, and passion — forged every day on the field.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('enroll').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Join the Academy</button>
    <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('programs').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">View Programs</button>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">500<span>+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Players Trained</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">12<span>+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Expert Coaches</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">8<span>+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Years of Excellence</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">30<span>+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Trophies Won</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-wrapper">
  <div class="marquee-track">
    <span class="marquee-item">Bagphat Football Academy</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">⚽</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Skill Development</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">★</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Youth Excellence</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">⚽</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Champions in the Making</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">★</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Discipline &amp; Teamwork</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">⚽</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Bagphat Football Academy</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">★</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Skill Development</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">⚽</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Youth Excellence</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">★</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Champions in the Making</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">⚽</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Discipline &amp; Teamwork</span>
    <span class="marquee-dot">★</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROGRAMS -->
<section id="programs">
  <div class="programs-header">
    <div>
      <div class="section-tag">Training Programs</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Choose Your Path</h2>
    </div>
    <p style="color:var(--grey);max-width:300px;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">
      Age-appropriate training programs designed to develop every aspect of the game.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="programs-grid">
    <div class="program-card">
      <div class="program-num">01</div>
      <div class="program-icon">🌱</div>
      <div class="program-name">Grassroots</div>
      <p class="program-desc">Introduction to football fundamentals — dribbling, passing, and the love of the beautiful game. Fun-first approach.</p>
      <div class="program-age">Ages 5 – 9</div>
    </div>
    <div class="program-card">
      <div class="program-num">02</div>
      <div class="program-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="program-name">Junior Elite</div>
      <p class="program-desc">Structured technical development with positional awareness, tactical understanding, and competitive match play.</p>
      <div class="program-age">Ages 10 – 14</div>
    </div>
    <div class="program-card">
      <div class="program-num">03</div>
      <div class="program-icon">🏆</div>
      <div class="program-name">Senior Academy</div>
      <p class="program-desc">High-performance training preparing players for district and state level competitions. Strength, fitness, and tactics.</p>
      <div class="program-age">Ages 15 – 19</div>
    </div>
    <div class="program-card">
      <div class="program-num">04</div>
      <div class="program-icon">🥅</div>
      <div class="program-name">Goalkeeping</div>
      <p class="program-desc">Specialist goalkeeper training covering shot-stopping, distribution, command of the box, and mental resilience.</p>
      <div class="program-age">All Ages</div>
    </div>
    <div class="program-card">
      <div class="program-num">05</div>
      <div class="program-icon">👩‍🦰</div>
      <div class="program-name">Girls Program</div>
      <p class="program-desc">Dedicated women's football development with a focus on empowerment, skill, and building a strong team culture.</p>
      <div class="program-age">Ages 8 – 18</div>
    </div>
    <div class="program-card">
      <div class="program-num">06</div>
      <div class="program-icon">🎯</div>
      <div class="program-name">Elite Camps</div>
      <p class="program-desc">Intensive holiday and weekend camps for players looking to accelerate their development outside of term-time.</p>
      <div class="program-age">Seasonal</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-visual">
    <div class="about-box">⚽</div>
    <div class="about-accent"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="section-tag">About the Academy</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">More Than a<br>Football Club</h2>
    <p class="about-text">
      Founded in Bagphat, Uttar Pradesh, our academy was built on the belief that every child in the region deserves access to world-class football coaching. We've been shaping players and characters for over 8 years.
    </p>
    <p class="about-text">
      Our certified coaches bring professional experience and a deep passion for developing young talent — not just on the pitch, but as individuals ready for life's challenges.
